# GitHub Personal Access Token used server-side to call the GitHub API.
# A fine-grained token with read-only public access is enough (no scopes
# required for public follower data). Create one at:
# https://github.com/settings/tokens
#
# This is a SERVER-ONLY variable — do NOT prefix it with VITE_, or it would be
# inlined into the client bundle.
GITHUB_TOKEN=
